content: My family members are all pretty diverse, so it's a bit hard to pinpoint specific interests or hobbies. But I do know my mom loves cozy things, my dad is into tech, and my niece is really into fashion. As for budget, I'd say around $50-100 per person, depending on the gift. And yeah, I've got a pretty big family, including parents, siblings, nieces, nephews, and some close family friends.
